create project folder
VSCode terminal>
    create server.js
    npm install express
    npm install body-parser
    npm install mongoose
    npm install fs
    //npm install express-session if needed
create angular project/ side terminal
    nav to project folder
    ng new public
    cd public
    ng build --watch
create routes/controller/models/mongoose .js files
create service
    nav to the angular app in the VSCode terminal
    ng g s http
register the service
    instructions in the platform: Angular>Fetch Data
    basically just referencing your new files
